Package ta4_1.MoneyFlow_Backend.Users

Class User

java.lang.Object
ta4_1.MoneyFlow_Backend.Users.User
@Entity public class User extends Object
Provides the Definition/Structure for the user table Represents a User in the MoneyFlow application. Each user has a unique ID, personal information, an income, associated expenses, and a list of cards.
